title: Help Please
body: Hey my friends can somehow see who my other friends are how are they doing this

replies.body: Your friends list should be provide, so I don't believe there is a way to actually see that.  Instead, they could be looking at your match history and looking for players you may be queuing up with.  Hopefully that provides some relief!
That's not true. Match history for normal games will only show players who are friends with the logged in account.
